all the stones and bushes.

561
00:53:14,577 --> 00:53:16,306
Is that clear?
- Yes.

562
00:53:29,024 --> 00:53:31,822
It's 7 feet and 6 inches.

563
00:54:07,229 --> 00:54:08,526
Shall I try it?

564
