571
00:55:10,125 --> 00:55:12,389
Ballu, show him an
alternator powered 24 watts.

572
00:55:12,628 --> 00:55:13,959
Please come in sir.

573
00:55:43,325 --> 00:55:47,022
Here's your water, Dadaji.
- Thank you, Santaram.

574
00:55:47,496 --> 00:55:49,794
How's the work progressing on the hill?

575
00:55:49,999 --> 00:55:51,227
It's getting on perfectly fine.

576
00:55:51,500 --> 00:55:54,128
