Electricity.

657
01:09:14,069 --> 01:09:16,663
Mohanbabu, we have done it.

658
01:09:16,905 --> 01:09:20,671
Electricity of our own village!
Generated with our toil and sweat.

659
01:09:21,076 --> 01:09:24,705
Just like this project, we must
think of newer and innovative ways

660
01:09:24,913 --> 01:09:27,006
to solve our village problems.

661
01:09:27,248 --> 01:09:32,447
Sarpanchji, come quickly!
Dadaji's health has deteriorated.

662
01:09:44,933 --> 01:09:46,195
Dadaji...

663
01:09:53,108 --> 01:09:55,474
Electricity? Is it here?

664
01:09:57,112 --> 01:09:58,374
Yes.

665
01:10:04,119 --> 01:10:05,780
The day...

666
01:10:06,287 --> 01:10:07,720
... I saw you...

667
01:10:09,124 --> 01:10:10,216
... I felt...

668
01:10:11,793 --> 01:10:15,854
... something special about you...

669
01:10:23,805 --> 01:10:25,568
Now that you're here...

670
01:10:27,475 --> 01:10:29,443
... I can...

671
01:10:29,911 --> 01:10:33,779
