There can't be any further delays!

675
01:11:54,729 --> 01:11:58,790
I understand John. I've just finished
what I needed to do here and

676
01:11:59,567 --> 01:12:01,159
I'll be back in three days.

677
01:12:01,569 --> 01:12:06,097
Three days it is!
- Of course John. Yes... I will.

678
01:12:27,929 --> 01:12:31,228
What surprises me is how you
can think of going

679
01:12:31,432 --> 01:12:34,230
after all that you have seen
and learnt here.

680
01:12:34,769 --> 01:12:36,031
It's true Gita.

681
01:12:36,604 --> 01:12:39,471
I have learnt so much here,
gained so much here.

682
01:12:39,941 --> 01:12:41,841
Felt the problems here...

683
01:12:43,444 --> 01:12:45,105
... but I cannot live here.

684
01:12:46,114 --> 01:12:48,412
And I cannot live out of this country.

685
01:12:51,286 --> 01:12:53,447
I am willing to marry you...

686
01:12:54,122 --> 01:12:56,249
... but I won't go to America.

687
01:13:17,478 --> 01:13:19,708
I know that you are not going to
come with me.

688
01:13:20,982 --> 01:13:24,645
Mohan, I've given it lot of thought.

689
01:13:25,820 --> 01:13:34,728
At this age, I'll not be able to adopt the
ways and customs of another country.

690
01:13:35,663 --> 01:13:40,157
I am happy here.

691
01:13:44,172 --> 01:13:46,037
Now that you are leaving...

692
01:13:49,344 --> 01:13:52,507
... I will miss you very much.

693
01:13:55,683 --> 01:13:59,380
If you were here, our family
would have been complete.

694
01:14:29,250 --> 01:14:30,444
I'll take your leave.

695
01:14:30,718 --> 01:14:32,117
May you live a long life son!

696
01:14:34,222 --> 01:14:37,419
We had forgotten that you were a guest.

697
01:14:37,725 --> 01:14:40,558
A visitor must leave one day.

698
01:14:47,735 --> 01:14:49,999
We'll miss you very much.

699
01:14:52,907 --> 01:14:54,499
When you come here next

700
01:14:54,742 --> 01:14:58,872
you'll surely find Internet
in Charanpur Post Office.

701
01:14:59,080 --> 01:15:01,344
Every little lad will email you.

702
01:15:02,083 --> 01:15:05,348
What we couldn't have,
is our wrestling match.

703
01:15:10,091 --> 01:15:13,822
I am sorry Mela Ram that
I have to leave suddenly.

704
01:15:14,095 --> 01:15:17,553
But I'll surely send you
the sponsorship papers.

705
01:15:18,433 --> 01:15:21,368
I don't need them anymore.
I'll be fine here.

706
01:15:22,770 --> 01:15:26,399
Your presence in the village has
changed some things around here.

707
01:15:26,774 --> 01:15:28,503
Some things have definitely changed.

708
01:15:28,776 --> 01:15:31,870
But you had planned your migration.

709
01:15:32,113 --> 01:15:35,913
When the creeper in your house crosses
into your neighbor's compound...

710
01:15:36,117 --> 01:15:38,312
... one's own house is ruined.

711
01:15:38,619 --> 01:15:45,149
It's like a lamp on your threshold
giving light to the neighbour's house.

712
01:15:45,460 --> 01:15:47,018
All the best Sir.

713
01:15:48,196 --> 01:15:49,754
Thank you Mela Ram.

714
01:16:02,143 --> 01:16:04,907
Mohanbhaiyya, this is for you.

715
01:16:12,653 --> 01:16:14,416
I will put this up in my house.

716
01:16:14,789 --> 01:16:18,122
Listen, study well.
Right!

717
01:16:38,179 --> 01:16:39,271
Where is Gita?

718
01:16:39,680 --> 01:16:42,444
I haven't seen her around since morning.

719
01:16:44,852 --> 01:16:46,217
I have to leave now.

720
01:16:46,521 --> 01:16:49,081
Or else I'll miss my flight.
- Ok.

721
01:16:49,690 --> 01:16:51,351
Please explain to her, ok?

722
01:16:54,529 --> 01:17:02,800
Go son! My love and blessings
are always with you.

723
01:17:10,211 --> 01:17:12,111
Don't worry...

724
01:17:19,220 --> 01:17:20,619
Bye.

725
01:18:13,274 --> 01:18:14,832
Gita, you're impossible!

726
01:18:15,109 --> 01:18:16,633
You're here and...

727
01:18:17,612 --> 01:18:19,944
